   "text": "SYNCHRONOUS  (default)\nreview \u2192 THEN voice.\nViolation PREVENTED before it's\nvoiced. NLI (~0.9s on clean\ncommittal turns) sits ON the\nfirst-audio path.",
   "fontSize": 11,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "center",
   "verticalAlign": "middle",
   "containerId": "r1069",
   "originalText": "SYNCHRONOUS  (default)\nreview \u2192 THEN voice.\nViolation PREVENTED before it's\nvoiced. NLI (~0.9s on clean\ncommittal turns) sits ON the\nfirst-audio path.",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 11
